@raffone  FWIW, Here's a LESS snippet I use to customize it, pretty compact, maybe would be useful for you if use LESS or SASS:
``` less
/ ==========================================================================
   SHARE WIDGET
   ========================================================================== /
.share-widget-overrides() {
    background: white;
    color: red;
    border-radius: 0;
.transition(all 0.1s ease);

span {
    font-family: "Raleway";
    font-weight: 800;
}

&:hover {
    background: red;
    color: white;
}

}
.share-button.sharer-0 label {
    .share-widget-overrides() !important;
} 
```
